# Flip Phone Resale Website

A static website for **Flip Phone Resale**, a small business specializing in buying, refurbishing, and reselling electronics.  
This site includes a storefront, cart, checkout flow, and a form for customers to sell their devices.

![Deploy to GitHub Pages](https://img.shields.io/badge/deployed-GitHub%20Pages-blue?logo=github)

---

## ğŸš€ Features
- Homepage with hero banner, highlights, and featured products
- Shop page with product grid and â€œAdd to Cartâ€ functionality
- Cart page with item list, remove/clear buttons, and total calculation
- Checkout page with order summary and confirmation message
- Sell page with form for customers to submit devices for quotes
- About page with business story, contact info, and hours
- Reusable header/footer with logo and navigation
- Responsive design with modern CSS grid and flexbox
- LocalStorage cart (no backend required)

